title: Survivor FPS (DayZ Clone)
description:
SURVIVOR FPS FEATURES
* A world full of zombies!
* Handguns, rifles and assault weapons
* Drivable Vehicles
* A large landscape to explore
* PVP Combat
*Food and Thirst system
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


The game is multiplayer only, and YES! You can play online!! ^_-


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Installation instructions:

-Extract & Play!


Remember to seed!! >:(


Oooohh and the game will ask for a serial key once you click mutiplayer but you don't need one just leave that spot blank and click play!



Enjoy! ^_-
